snippet.title: The Fall of the Dungeon Guardians   Gameplay Final #2 (Boss with Active Pause)
snippet.description:
Here a gameplay video of the final version of The Fall of the Dungeon Guardians, a Dungeon Crawler for Windows / Mac / Linux.

This is a long fight against a though boss !

More info : http://www.managames.com/DungeonGuardians/about/
Blog : http://www.managames.com/DungeonGuardians
